message:
Add guest mode and fix TypeScript errors

Features:
- Add "Continue as Guest" button to login screen
- Block image generation for guests (requires login)
- Block analysis/reflections for guests (requires login)
- Fix "Start Fresh" to work for both authenticated and guest users

Code cleanup:
- Remove unused imports (generateDailyPicture, saveDailyPicture from App.tsx)
- Fix private property access (use getState() instead of .state)
- Fix migration data type (convert null to undefined)
- Fix React import type (use type-only import for ReactNode)

All TypeScript errors resolved. Build passing.
